message.body: Hey! Just got out of the pool. How are u feeling?
Much better, thank you :-) Wounds not quite there yet, but healing finally. Something is still off with my wrist, but at least it's better than before
Might be in for tomorrow night! Text me when you'd like to go :-)
Sounds like a plan! Prob sometime around 8-8:30 would work, if this is not too late.
